com.hp.hpl.jena.sparql.util
Class IndentedLineBuffer

java.lang.Object
  com.hp.hpl.jena.sparql.util.IndentedLineBuffer

public class IndentedLineBuffer
extends java.lang.Object

IndentLineBuffer is a buffer that records an indent level and uses that to insert a prefix at each line. It can also insert line numbers at the beginning of lines. Also, Java 1.5, StringBuilding is fatser than StringBuffer (not sync'ed) so could switch to that (exxept we are really using a StringWriter)

Author:
Andy Seaborne
